    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 1849 年淘金热期间，开始一场前往荒野西部心脏的旅程。 Forty-Niner 是一款将生存、角色扮演深度和沙盒自由结合在一起，打造出真正沉浸式的西部生存体验的游戏。游戏邀请您留下印记，并在一个不断发展的世界中塑造自己的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >活力四射的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个由程序生成的充满生机、生态群落丰富且气候动态的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/2d3d4f4f5bf3ff5f180c87bf5c151c03.poster.avif?t=1749582427\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/2d3d4f4f5bf3ff5f180c87bf5c151c03.webm?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/2d3d4f4f5bf3ff5f180c87bf5c151c03.mp4?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作、战斗和探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从深入地下洞穴到湍急的河流，收集资源、制作武器并保卫你的领土，这片土地机会多多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/b8d56eddc3c78338085b741d3488cb0b.poster.avif?t=1749582427\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/b8d56eddc3c78338085b741d3488cb0b.webm?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/b8d56eddc3c78338085b741d3488cb0b.mp4?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立你的家园</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用你在世界各地找到的资源，建立并个性化你的基地，从简陋的帐篷到繁忙的酒吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/1bd874d04bf4fc9be2d8c333067391d6.poster.avif?t=1749582427\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/1bd874d04bf4fc9be2d8c333067391d6.webm?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/1bd874d04bf4fc9be2d8c333067391d6.mp4?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >形塑你的世界的动态 NPC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与一个每个 NPC 都有自己生活和日程安排的世界。与其他旅行者竞争，或在夜晚在舒适的酒吧里休息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/26f7191600a2b1afaadf38b93cad9cb8.poster.avif?t=1749582427\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/26f7191600a2b1afaadf38b93cad9cb8.webm?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/26f7191600a2b1afaadf38b93cad9cb8.mp4?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人或合作冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自体验淘金热的刺激，或与朋友们联手，探索一个无尽可能性的广阔世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/4a041a0d382a4fd06068c2f182575c5b.poster.avif?t=1749582427\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/4a041a0d382a4fd06068c2f182575c5b.webm?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/4a041a0d382a4fd06068c2f182575c5b.mp4?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >按自己的方式扮演角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的道路，是牛仔还是土著美国人，每个都有独特的技能和任务，在丰富的角色扮演体验中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/f24858be045b0fd41584bc6e78ac30a3.poster.avif?t=1749582427\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/f24858be045b0fd41584bc6e78ac30a3.webm?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379820/extras/f24858be045b0fd41584bc6e78ac30a3.mp4?t=1749582427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸式技能系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握丰富的技能进展系统，通过任务和挑战增强你的能力，并在其他先驱者中脱颖而出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现在将 Forty-Niner 加入愿望清单，成为塑造边疆的社区的一部分，并获得早期支持者的独家奖励。</strong></p>",
